  "body": "Bugfixes:\r\n* Fix max CPU frequency detection for some cases (CPU, Linux)\r\n* Fix some memory leaks\r\n* Fix ddcutil 2.1 compatibility (Brightness, Linux)\r\n* Workaround `permission denied` error when reading `/proc/uptime` (Uptime, Android)\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n* Support zellij version detection (Linux, Terminal)\r\n\r\nLogo:\r\n* Fix PostMarketOS\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<details><summary>SHA256SUMs</summary><br>\r\n\r\n```\r\n751b0c4639e9d18f975bed6dcd409f36276c5255a7dead633ad87c9b7b8e508f  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.tar.gz\r\nbbcf5d32eab0b1821be43a194733e91b012a2393b39eef3426b8bdcd0d8552f8  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.zip\r\n22e6ccef99324cea831320876a88f2715a6bcbbe8b2e4b1d178e378d1754125e  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.tar.gz\r\n8b096a2faf51e59aab422631fec0777d4192925f8193b616f9a1670c136ba09e  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.zip\r\n964851b74875c830ee11f6e8b67ddf92533b26067127082439a10118f15bd2eb  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.deb\r\n84a5031f8382db6e50cb80dd01396df8914cfa0f82406063dfca2a6b02111bd7  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.rpm\r\n29acdededc29137205d8fe9af3aeef974cb9d5e7da4cd63573a74449fbe3aa57  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.tar.gz\r\n269b82e7fe0d792522f5e7043fc183d07dd0e5b8d4141d79032b02b64507e2c7  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.zip\r\n6cf29b6d64029df0c9a41064150b8121926bf127e6851bfdf0483f8a8dd352c5  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.deb\r\n560adba2e971d879bf8507722bd44f3a5d96ac13dbff972608b73b722881851f  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.rpm\r\n7267a36139af9872856d566ef19abdbfe045e8e4d995fcddf1b450d3604b9ae6  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.tar.gz\r\n764ef54cee46fdc6408f6fec6ef5c42dfe1b33db27ccb50c879d99d8334aedfe  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.zip\r\n3a9cae3dd1f1eba7f3116b2bca731828e3b848078d519b64aa86b20e39fef46f  fastfetch-macos-universal/fastfetch-mac